  "title": "Class 4 Delivery Driver - Kranji (OT provided)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan route and estimates travel times</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely collection &amp; delivery of goods</li>\n  <li>Assisting in loading / unloading of goods</li>\n  <li>Maintain and ensure cleanliness of company vehicle</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess class 4 driving license</li>\n  <li>Excellent organizational and time management skills</li>\n  <li>Clean Driving Record</li>\n  <li>Willing to work OT and weekend (OT Pay is provided)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
